<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 01:24:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>OHSU 研究揭示胰腺癌如何阻碍免疫治疗</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ohsu-research-reveals-how-pancreatic-cancer-blocks-immunotherapy</link><description>研究还确定了免疫疗法有效对抗致命的、难治性癌症的潜在途径。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ohsu-research-reveals-how-pancreatic-cancer-blocks-immunotherapy.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 01:24:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ohsu-research-reveals-how-pancreatic-cancer-blocks-immunotherapy</guid></item><item><title>增殖和凋亡衔接蛋白 15 (PEA15)，通过肝细胞癌蛋白质组学分析鉴定出的 VHL 和 HIF1A 潜在致癌调节因子</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/proliferation-and-apoptosis-adaptor-protein-15-pea15-a-potential-oncogenic-regulator-of-vhl-and-hif1a-identified-through-proteomic-analysis-in-hepatocellular-carcinoma</link><description>刚刚发布：单击此处阅读 Cancer Communications 最新的免费开放获取文章。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/proliferation-and-apoptosis-adaptor-protein-15-pea15-a-potential-oncogenic-regulator-of-vhl-and-hif1a-identified-through-proteomic-analysis-in-hepatocellular-carcinoma.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 01:09:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/proliferation-and-apoptosis-adaptor-protein-15-pea15-a-potential-oncogenic-regulator-of-vhl-and-hif1a-identified-through-proteomic-analysis-in-hepatocellular-carcinoma</guid></item><item><title>NIH 资助的突破性成果缩小了 CRISPR 在体内的精确递送</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/nih-funded-breakthrough-shrinks-crispr-for-precision-delivery-in-the-body</link><description>更小的基因编辑系统可以扩大癌症、ALS 和其他疾病的治疗选择。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nih-funded-breakthrough-shrinks-crispr-for-precision-delivery-in-the-body.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 00:54:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/nih-funded-breakthrough-shrinks-crispr-for-precision-delivery-in-the-body</guid></item><item><title>摘要：在前列腺癌中，雄激素受体剪接变异可促进治疗抵抗和疾病进展</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/abstract-in-prostatecancer-treatment-resistance-and-disease-progression-can-be-promoted-by-androgen-receptor-splice-variants</link><description>Johann de Bono、Luke Gaughan 和团队在此发现蛋白质 TRA2B 是 AR-V 合成的关键。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/abstract124.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 00:39:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/abstract-in-prostatecancer-treatment-resistance-and-disease-progression-can-be-promoted-by-androgen-receptor-splice-variants</guid></item><item><title>新型牙膏可预防牙龈疾病而不杀死有益细菌</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-toothpaste-stops-gum-disease-without-killing-good-bacteria</link><description>科学家们开发出一种新方法来对抗牙龈疾病，而无需消灭口腔中的有益细菌，这是传统治疗方法的重大转变。这种有针对性的方法不会杀死所有细菌，而是只阻止导致牙周炎的有害微生物，让有益细菌繁殖并自然恢复平衡。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-toothpaste-stops-gum-disease-without-killing-good-bacteria.webp" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 00:24:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-toothpaste-stops-gum-disease-without-killing-good-bacteria</guid></item><item><title>动物研究表明，实验药物可以在几周内逆转骨关节炎</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/experimental-drug-can-reverse-osteoarthritis-in-weeks-animal-research-shows</link><description>关节软骨的慢性丧失使人衰弱&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/experimental-drug-can-reverse-osteoarthritis-in-weeks-animal-research-shows.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 00:09:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/experimental-drug-can-reverse-osteoarthritis-in-weeks-animal-research-shows</guid></item><item><title>TgFbox1-TgNAC2-TgWIN1模块通过微调郁金香表皮蜡生物合成来调节花瓣衰老</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/tgfbox1-tgnac2-tgwin1-module-regulates-petal-senescence-by-fine-tuning-cuticular-wax-biosynthesis-in-tulip</link><description>微调花瓣衰老对于控制花朵寿命和遗传改良至关重要。杨等人。提出一个&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tgfbox1-tgnac2-tgwin1-module-regulates-petal-senescence-by-fine-tuning-cuticular-wax-biosynthesis-in-tulip2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 23:54:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/tgfbox1-tgnac2-tgwin1-module-regulates-petal-senescence-by-fine-tuning-cuticular-wax-biosynthesis-in-tulip</guid></item><item><title>科学家称宇宙最终将分裂</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-say-the-universe-will-eventually-tear-itself-apart</link><description>放松，这只发生在理论物理学中——至少目前是这样。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-say-the-universe-will-eventually-tear-itself-apart.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 23:39:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-say-the-universe-will-eventually-tear-itself-apart</guid></item><item><title>新型内存芯片可承受 1300°F 的高温，比熔岩还热</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-memory-chip-survives-1300f-hotter-than-lava</link><description>电子产品通常会在极端高温下失效，但科学家们现在发明了一种存储芯片，可以在比熔岩更热的温度下保持工作。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-memory-chip-survives-1300f-hotter-than-lava.jpg" /&gt; 由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 23:24:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/new-memory-chip-survives-1300f-hotter-than-lava</guid></item><item><title>以前未被认识的免疫反应可以增强对癌症的防御</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/previously-unrecognized-immune-response-could-enhance-defense-against-cancer</link><description>在一项突破范式的研究中，研究人员发现了免疫系统（特别是 T 细胞）攻击靶细胞的一种新方式，重塑了免疫学领域长期以来的假设，并证明了对癌症免疫学和骨髓移植领域的直接影响。该团队由贝勒医学院 (BCM) Dan L Duncan 综合癌症中心主任 Pavan Reddy 博士及其团队组成，并与 Drs. Arul Chinnaiyan（SP Hicks 捐赠病理学教授）和 Marcin Cieslik（病理学助理教授）均来自密歇根大学罗格尔癌症中心。该研究发表在《自然免疫学》上。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/previously-unrecognized-immune-response-could-enhance-defense-against-cancer2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 Apr 2026 23:09:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/previously-unrecognized-immune-response-could-enhance-defense-against-cancer</guid></item></channel></rss>